FBIS4-3820 "drchi079_k_94001" FBIS-CHI-94-079 Daily Report 23 Apr 1994 NATIONAL AFFAIRS Political & Social Spokesman Reports Wang Juntao Released on Bail for Treatment Spokesman Reports Wang Juntao Released on Bail for Treatment OW2304084994 Beijing XINHUA in English 0835 GMT 23 Apr 94 OW2304084994 Beijing XINHUA English BFN [Text] Beijing, April 23 (XINHUA) -- Wang Juntao, who had been in custody, has left for medical treatment abroad after the Chinese judicial authorities released him on bail according to law on account of the conditions of his illness, a spokesman for the Ministry of Justice said here today. The spokesman was answering a question from a reporter on the release of Wang Juntao.
